    I used to hold.

    Since you went a -- way
    the days grow long,
    And soon I'll hear 
    old win -- ter's song, 

    But I miss you most of all,
    my dar -- ling,

    When au -- tumn leaves 
    start to fall.
}
lyricsHeadTwo = \lyricmode {
    \override LyricText.font-family = #'typewriter
